import React from 'react'
import { CContainer } from '@coreui/react'

const Checkout = () => {
  return (
             <>
                    <CContainer fluid>
                    <CRow>
                            <CCol>1 of 2</CCol>
                            <CCol>2 of 2</CCol>
  </CRow>
                    </CContainer>  
             </>
  )
}

export default Checkout
